WEBVTT

00:00:29.542 --> 00:00:33.351
you can probably choose
between several different types of fish.

00:00:33.375 --> 00:00:35.934
But chances are,
they won't be able to tell you

00:00:35.958 --> 00:00:39.101
who caught the fish,
where precisely it was caught,

00:00:39.125 --> 00:00:41.393
whether it is sustainable
to catch it there

00:00:41.417 --> 00:00:43.458
and how it got transported.

00:00:44.083 --> 00:00:46.976
And that holds true
for almost everything we buy.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.768
Every can of soup,

00:00:48.792 --> 00:00:51.309
every piece of meat, every T-shirt.

00:00:51.333 --> 00:00:53.601
We as humans, right now,

00:00:53.625 --> 00:00:57.143
are destroying the only thing
we really need to survive:

00:00:57.167 --> 00:00:58.434
our planet.

00:00:58.458 --> 00:01:01.476
And most of the horrible problems
that we're facing today,